07 AM - 08 PM
We have 14 powered camping sites that has 16A power outlets that can be used for charging vehicles while staying camping or just passing for a cup of coffee or buying products in our small provision store. Charging for the day only is $4 and if you are camping it is $6 for each night you stay. We have amazing views over the islands and you are welcome to have a relaxing moment while adding power to continue your journey.
